{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-tipping-content-js","path":"/hungary","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>Tips (<em>borravaló</em>) are given in Hungary for some services: in restaurants, in bars, to taxi drivers, to hairdressers, and often to people that fix things around the house, like plumbers and electricians.</p>\n<p>Although not legally required, social norms encourage that tips are given. 10% is usually enough. Check your receipt before you pay, because some bars and restaurants charge a 10% service fee (szervizdíj), in this case tipping is not expected.</p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/hungary","title":"Hungary","author":"Joni","date":"2019-11-22","image":"hungary.jpg"}},"image":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/jpeg;base64,","aspectRatio":1.7774538386783285,"src":"/static/3b6d856b02315c08ce8545988c353865/90537/hungary.jpg","srcSet":"/static/3b6d856b02315c08ce8545988c353865/b3ebb/hungary.jpg 270w,\n/static/3b6d856b02315c08ce8545988c353865/95b54/hungary.jpg 540w,\n/static/3b6d856b02315c08ce8545988c353865/90537/hungary.jpg 1080w,\n/static/3b6d856b02315c08ce8545988c353865/3cda3/hungary.jpg 1620w,\n/static/3b6d856b02315c08ce8545988c353865/1f682/hungary.jpg 2160w,\n/static/3b6d856b02315c08ce8545988c353865/d6cdf/hungary.jpg 5487w","sizes":"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px"}}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"image":"hungary.jpg"}}}